Dialogue: 4,0:00:05.81,0:00:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Onee-chan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:07.71,0:00:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her little brother, attempting to reach his older sister, Chihaya,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:11.06,0:00:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}was hit by a car and \Ndeparted this world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:15.09,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chihaya was eight at the time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:18.20,0:00:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to testimony \Nfrom those at the scene,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:21.13,0:00:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chihaya didn't even try to \Nhelp her little brother.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:24.05,0:00:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She merely watched from afar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:00:27.29,0:00:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did she simply \Nwatch her brother die?{\i0}
