Dialogue: 4,0:05:50.08,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, are you \Nthere? It's Haruka.
Dialogue: 4,0:05:58.41,0:05:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need something?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:00.67,0:06:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:01.95,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering if you want to go to dance lessons together.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:07.64,0:06:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it feels good when \Nyou get your body moving!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:11.51,0:06:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:15.29,0:06:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have some things from everyone.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:17.85,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like tea, and throat lozenges \Nand all sorts of stuff.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told them, "I can't carry all of that!"
Dialogue: 4,0:06:23.37,0:06:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they kept going, \N"And this! And this!"
Dialogue: 4,0:06:25.66,0:06:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel kinda like Santa Claus!
Dialogue: 4,0:06:28.41,0:06:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing anymore.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:34.73,0:06:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't respond to \Neveryone's expectations.
Dialogue: 4,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan...
Dialogue: 4,0:06:41.78,0:06:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, didn't you say you had to keep singing for your little brother?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't it be a little \Nsimpler than that?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:50.04,0:06:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because I love to sing."
Dialogue: 4,0:06:51.83,0:06:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you sing just \Nbecause you love to sing?
Dialogue: 4,0:06:58.61,0:07:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see it like that \Nafter all this time.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:03.39,0:07:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan, don't you think you're \Nputting too much pressure on yourself?
Dialogue: 4,0:07:07.86,0:07:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y–You should just say, \N"I'll sing because I want to!"
Dialogue: 4,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easier on your feelings!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 4,0:07:16.69,0:07:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, if we could all sing \Ntogether again, we'd all be so happy...
Dialogue: 4,0:07:22.28,0:07:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I just know your little brother up in Heaven would also–
Dialogue: 4,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka, my feelings aren't–
Dialogue: 4,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuu's feelings aren't \Nsomething you could understand!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:33.30,0:07:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being such a good Samaritan!
Dialogue: 4,0:07:58.59,0:08:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Amami Haruka-san, aren't you?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:08.09,0:08:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kisaragi Chihaya's mother.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:13.85,0:08:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you'd like, the office is–
Dialogue: 4,0:08:21.69,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's all right.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:25.97,0:08:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U–Um...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.48,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 4,0:08:28.25,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
