Dialogue: 4,0:08:33.54,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pass this on to Chihaya?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:39.04,0:08:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my departed son's sketchbook.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:43.68,0:08:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's little brother's?
Dialogue: 4,0:08:47.93,0:08:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son truly loved \Nto hear Chihaya sing.
Dialogue: 4,0:08:51.91,0:08:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd go on and on... "Sing! Sing!"
Dialogue: 4,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she recalled the period \Nwhen they were close,
Dialogue: 4,0:08:58.78,0:09:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then maybe Chihaya could...
Dialogue: 4,0:09:00.80,0:09:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:02.22,0:09:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, rather than having \Nme give it to her,
Dialogue: 4,0:09:05.31,0:09:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think her mother \Nshould give it to her!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:07.89,0:09:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that way she would–
Dialogue: 4,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I–
Dialogue: 4,0:09:12.74,0:09:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we were to see one another, \Nwe'd surely just end up fighting.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:17.55,0:09:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B–But even when I tried to \Ncheer her up, I couldn't do it!
Dialogue: 4,0:09:23.19,0:09:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So instead of me, \NI'm sure her mother could–
Dialogue: 4,0:09:27.55,0:09:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:30.35,0:09:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't expect to regain \Nher trust after all this time.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:34.98,0:09:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our relationship has \Nalways been like this.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:40.26,0:09:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Stop being such a good Samaritan!{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is just about all I can do.
Dialogue: 4,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch over her in my stead.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:00.53,0:10:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she gave this to you and left?
