Dialogue: 4,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I see.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:07.68,0:10:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}We'll have to take care \Nof Chihaya after all.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Haruka?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:15.75,0:10:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You look pretty down.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:18.51,0:10:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:23.27,0:10:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um... do I come off \Nas a "good Samaritan"?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd that come \Nfrom all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 4,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan said so...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:37.46,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said to "Stop being \Nsuch a good Samaritan."
Dialogue: 4,0:10:42.20,0:10:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always saying, "Let's do \Nour best!" "Let's do our best!"
Dialogue: 4,0:10:46.73,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just to Chihaya-chan, \Nbut to everyone else, too.
Dialogue: 4,0:10:50.81,0:10:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if everybody \Nwanted me to mind my own business...
Dialogue: 4,0:10:56.38,0:10:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 4,0:10:59.40,0:11:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your optimism is your strong point!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:03.53,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be considerate all the time when you cheer someone up!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:07.16,0:11:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:08.93,0:11:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really happy when you gave me that caramel back then.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:14.79,0:11:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really just wanted to start \Nover as everyone's friend.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:21.41,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciated that, Haruka.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer-san...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, Haruka...
Dialogue: 4,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya might be a little awkward,
Dialogue: 4,0:11:31.89,0:11:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think she's someone who really does understand peoples' feelings.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:34.87,0:11:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then everything's fine.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:38.14,0:11:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings have definitely \Ngotten through to her.
Dialogue: 4,0:11:41.07,0:11:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and hit her with \Neverything you're feeling!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:47.19,0:11:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 4,0:11:57.94,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's in every last one, holding a mic and smiling.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:02.58,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you draw those, Haruka?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:05.14,0:12:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not me.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:08.75,0:12:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan's brother did.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:13.57,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So these are Chihaya-san?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:15.52,0:12:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:17.31,0:12:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:18.62,0:12:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've ever seen \NChihaya-san sing like this.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't either, Miki?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:25.19,0:12:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:29.30,0:12:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I must continue to sing."{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:12:31.50,0:12:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I've got to keep singing. For Yuu."{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:12:39.90,0:12:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I want to leave Chihaya's \Nspot until the last minute.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if she loses it in front of the fans,
Dialogue: 4,0:12:47.09,0:12:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,won't that really make \Nher lose all confidence...?
Dialogue: 4,0:12:49.49,0:12:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:50.95,0:12:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we have a chance before \Nshe convinces herself she can't do it.
Dialogue: 4,0:12:55.81,0:12:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if it's the regular concert, \Nthe risk won't be too...
Dialogue: 4,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer-san!
Dialogue: 4,0:13:00.00,0:13:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:01.48,0:13:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I want your opinion on something.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:07.00,0:13:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Kisaragi Chihaya \Nis still on a leave of absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.26,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz341.609\fax0.3\pos(885,178)}{ts|13.08|Hanging sign 1/2 (black/red)}{\bord5\c&HC59565&\3c&HF6F8FA&}THE TRUTH {\c&HF0F4F6&\3c&H393D3F&}BEHIND \N{\3c&H4947CE&\c&H3F4148&}KISARAGI CHIHAYA'S SILENCE
Dialogue: 4,0:13:11.24,0:13:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's see...
Dialogue: 4,0:13:13.01,0:13:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When things stretch into \Nthis long a time-frame–
Dialogue: 4,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan...?
Dialogue: 4,0:13:45.73,0:13:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:50.77,0:13:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, there's something \NI wanted to give you today.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:54.49,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you open the door?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.44,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H2F3B53&\fs14\fnIwata Gyousho Pro-Kami B\pos(752.5,102.5)\fay-0.19}{ts|05.41|Pin-pon}Kisaragi
Dialogue: 4,0:13:57.85,0:13:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 4,0:13:59.65,0:14:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave me alone.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:04.32,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you alone.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:06.59,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't leave you alone!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I want to keep \Nworking with you, Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:14.33,0:14:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to stand together \Nonstage and sing!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I am a "good Samaritan."
Dialogue: 4,0:14:21.16,0:14:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even then!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:24.15,0:14:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stay an idol!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:34.33,0:14:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll leave this in your mail slot.
Dialogue: 4,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you look at it!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:54.98,0:14:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dear Chihaya-chan,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:14:56.93,0:15:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a little sudden, \Nbut we have a new song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:00.57,0:15:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone at 765 Pro \Npitched in to write the lyrics,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:03.14,0:15:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we asked a composer \Nto set it to music.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:07.63,0:15:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We all thought of how we could convey our feelings to you,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:12.89,0:15:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and "Of course! Let's put it in music!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:15.92,0:15:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone was happy to help.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:19.18,0:15:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's our first time writing lyrics, \Nso they might not be very good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:25.17,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But each of us, one by one, placed our honest feelings for you into this song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:33.53,0:15:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If we could all sing this \Nsong we wrote together,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:37.50,0:15:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if we could get you to smile,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:42.79,0:15:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like the girl in the pictures \Nyour little brother drew...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.25,0:15:48.96,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnHelveticaRounded LT Std Bd\b1\fs40\fax0.05\c&H8B9CB8&\3c&H12417F&\bord4\pos(489,139)\frx8\fry354\frz35.911}{ts|15.46|Sketchbook top}Sketchbook
