Dialogue: 4,0:15:55.32,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also... you might get mad at me again,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.97,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEraserDustPL\fs72\frz37.035\pos(520,138)\be1\c&H3D3198&\fad(125,0)}{ts|15.56|Sketchbook page top right}Onee-chan {おねえちゃん - note the ゃん/an characters are both backwards, and the ん is on a different line because he ran out of room}
Dialogue: 4,0:15:59.93,0:16:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I wonder if your brother didn't \Nnecessarily just want to hear you sing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:04.23,0:16:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if he just wanted \Nto see you smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:12.61,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnEraserDustPL\fs72\be1\c&H1F252F&\frz322.366\pos(744,210)}{ts|16.08|Sketchbook page top right}Onee-chan {おねえちゃん - note the おね/one characters are backwards}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:08.30,0:16:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A girl who loves to sing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:10.15,0:16:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and when she sings, she smiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you think that's \Nthe big sister he loved?{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:24.03,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And finally, a P.S. \Nfrom Producer-san:{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:28.43,0:16:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"You're in the schedule \Nfor the regular concert.{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:32.29,0:16:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The fans, and we, are waitin' for ya."{\i0}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:35.54,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or so he says.{\i0}
