Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.96,INS-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,~a poker face with my lips
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.75,INS-ROM,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo toudai moto kurashi Do you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:44.75,INS-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! It's dark at the bottom of the lighthouse! Do you know!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:49.75,INS-ROM,,0000,0000,0000,,Girigiri de oazuke Funky girl
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:49.75,INS-TL,,0000,0000,0000,,That funky girl cuts bait just at the last moment {LINE NEEDS HALP}
Dialogue: 4,0:16:51.63,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That was fine for me.
Dialogue: 4,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me!
Dialogue: 4,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, I'm constantly \Non the verge of tripping up...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger. We'll check.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Please do!
