Dialogue: 4,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:15.96,0:17:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Chihaya...?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Not yet.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Chihaya won't–
Dialogue: 4,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:23.59,0:17:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's circle up like always!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:27.98,0:17:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,765 Pro–
Dialogue: 4,0:17:34.41,0:17:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S–Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:46.67,0:17:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:47.04,0:17:49.66,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-onee-chan!
Dialogue: 4,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya. I'm so glad you came.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Producer...
Dialogue: 4,0:17:54.94,0:17:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... Think you can do it?
Dialogue: 4,0:17:57.54,0:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 4,0:17:59.67,0:18:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at the very least, I–
Dialogue: 4,0:18:03.72,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruka...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya-chan.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:11.55,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's get that hand.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,765 Pro–
Dialogue: 4,0:18:18.03,0:18:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight–
Dialogue: 4,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah–
Dialogue: 4,0:18:23.27,0:18:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone! You having a good time?!
Dialogue: 4,0:18:30.29,0:18:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Haruka?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:32.67,0:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um... I said such terrible–
Dialogue: 4,0:18:37.14,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's not get into that! Okay?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:45.43,0:18:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought, "I want to sing,"
Dialogue: 4,0:18:49.34,0:18:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw the lyrics everyone \Nwrote together and Yuu's drawings...
Dialogue: 4,0:18:54.84,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:18:57.08,0:18:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll be able to smile?
Dialogue: 4,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I'll be \Nable to sing, though.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:03.61,0:19:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought to myself, \N"I want to give it another chance."
Dialogue: 4,0:19:07.47,0:19:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:17.52,0:19:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:18.48,0:19:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:20.04,0:19:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:22.03,0:19:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:23.20,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay relaxed.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:25.24,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're on.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:33.60,0:19:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 4,0:19:38.12,0:19:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Chihaya-chan!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:39.48,0:19:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chihaya?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:40.67,0:19:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's coming on today?
Dialogue: 4,0:19:43.68,0:19:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that even safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.63,0:19:59.30,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnHelveticaRounded LT Std Bd\b1\blur1\an3\fs40\bord4\3c&H5599C9&\c&HD7DCDE&\pos(173,428)}{ts|15.46|Sketchbook top}Sketchbook
