Dialogue: 4,0:20:13.84,0:20:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew she couldn't...!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Please stop \Neverything for a moment!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:19.15,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H–Haruka!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W–Wait!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:22.28,0:20:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 4,0:20:23.51,0:20:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let her.
Dialogue: 4,0:20:24.70,0:20:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let them keep going!
